    "theory": "DWSIM is a multiplatform, CAPE-OPEN compliant chemical process simulator. It uses rigorous thermodynamic and unit operations models to simulate process plants. The software features a modular thermodynamics engine available as a standalone DLL.",
    "source_url": "https://dwsim.fossee.in/",
    "license": "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "flag": "INCOMPLETE"
  },
