        "Calculation of missing data",
        "Optimization method selection",
        "Objective Function selection"
      ]
    },
    "ui_paths": [],
    "errors": [],
    "fixes": [],
    "theory": "Regression of experimental binary data for determination of interaction parameters for thermodynamic models using Objective Functions such as Least Squares of temperature/pressure plus vapor fractions.",
